'''Agrarian Trade Union Federation''' (in [[Spanish language|Spanish]]: ''Federación Sindical Agraria'') was a [[National syndicalism|national-syndicalist]] [[trade union]] in [[Spain]], founded in 1933 in [[Castile (historical region)|Castile]]. The federation was linked to the ''[[Juntas de Ofensiva Nacional-Sindicalista]]''.

