The '''Army Staff, Defence Command Denmark''' is the [[Royal Danish Army]]'s top authority, and directly under the [[Defence Command (Denmark)|Defence Command]]. It was created as part of the [[Danish Defence Agreement 2013–17]], which called for major restructuring within the Danish military.<ref name="ArmyStaff" /> It is the successor to [[Army Operational Command (Denmark)|Army Operational Command]].
