'''Balıkesir Airport''' {{airport codes|BZI|LTBF}} is a military airport in the city of [[Balıkesir]], [[Turkey]].<ref name=GCM />
==Military usage== Balıkesir is home to the 9th Air Wing (''Ana Jet Üs'' or ''AJÜ'') of the 1st Air Force Command (''Hava Kuvvet Komutanligi'') of the [[Turkish Air Force]] (''Türk Hava Kuvvetleri''). Other wings of this command are located in [[Eskişehir Airport|Eskişehir]] (LTBI), [[Konya Airport|Konya]] (LTAN), [[Akıncı Air Base|Ankara Akıncı]] (LTAE) and [[Bandirma Airport|Bandırma]] (LTBG).<ref>[http://www.scramble.nl/tr.htm Turkish Air Force] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071213000000/http://www.scramble.nl/tr.htm |date=December 13, 2007 }} - ''Scramble''</ref>
