'''Radio Melody'''  is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[radio broadcasting|radio station]], launched in 2007. It is part of '''[[bTV (Bulgaria)|BTV]] Media Group''' owned by [[Central European Media Enterprises]]. It airs only in [[Sofia]] and online. Its core audience is mainly older listeners and the station mainly plays music from the 1950s, 1960s, 1970s, 1980s and 1990s along with the best pop, classic Bulgarian and evergreen music.

