{{Orphan|date=February 2017}}

'''''Proč právě Zeman?''''' (English: ''Why Zeman?'') is a book by Czech authors [[Jan Herzmann]] and [[Martin Komárek]], about [[Miloš Zeman]]'s [[Czech presidential election, 2013|2013 presidential campaign]] and reasons for his victory. It was published in March 2013.<ref>{{cite web|title=KNIHA: Proč právě Zeman?|url=http://neviditelnypes.lidovky.cz/kniha-proc-prave-zeman-06u-/p_politika.aspx?c=A130311_100543_p_politika_wag|website=Lidovky.cz|accessdate=15 February 2017|date=13 March 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Proč právě Herzmann? Rozhovor s RNDr. J. Herzmannem, CSc., zakladatelem sociologické agentury Factum {{!}}|url=http://forumlibcice.cz/proc-prave-herzmann-rozhovor-s-rndr-j-herzmannem-csc-zakladatelem-sociologicke-agentury-factum/|website=forumlibcice.cz|accessdate=15 February 2017|language=cs-CZ}}</ref> The book follows the presidential candidates from the first round. The authors concluded that [[Karel Schwarzenberg]] was the ideal opponent for Zeman, as he never had a chance of beating him.<ref>{{cite web|title=Pro Zemana byl kníže ideální soupeř. Kniha ukazuje, že jej vždy porážel|url=http://www.parlamentnilisty.cz/arena/monitor/Pro-Zemana-byl-knize-idealni-souper-Kniha-ukazuje-ze-jej-vzdy-porazel-264502|website=Parlamentní Listy|accessdate=15 February 2017}}</ref>

